import React from "react";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";
import { useAuth } from "./context/auth";

function Navigation(props) {
    const { authTokens } = useAuth();

    return (
        <Navbar bg="primary" variant="dark" expand="md">
            <Navbar.Brand href="/">Barnwood Site</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
            authTokens ? (
                <Nav className="mr-auto">
                    <NavDropdown title="Products" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="/products">Product List</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Divider />
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="/products/new">Admin: Create Product</NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                    <Nav.Link href="/users">Admin: User List</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="/contact">Contact Us</Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
                <Nav>
                    <Nav.Link href="/logout">Log Out</Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
            ) : (
                <Nav className="mr-auto">
                    <NavDropdown title="Products" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="/products">Product List</NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                    <Nav.Link href="/contact">Contact Us</Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
                <Nav>
                    <Nav.Link href="/register">Register</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="/login">Login</Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
            )
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>
    )
}

export default Navigation;
